# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
`@angular/core`

### Is this a regression?

No, ViewEngine has same behavior.

### Description

A root component (or a dynamically inserted one) should be able to inject `ViewContainerRef` and than into that `ViewContainerRef` insert dynamic components.


## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction

```typescript

  fit('should work', () => {
    @Component({
      selector: 'dynamic',
      template: `DYNAMIC COMPONENT`,
    })
    class Dynamic {
    }

    @Component({
      selector: 'my-app',
      template: `MY APP`,
    })
    class AppComponent {
      constructor(
          public _vcRef: ViewContainerRef, public _cfr: ComponentFactoryResolver,
          public _injector: Injector) {
        appComponent = this;
      }
    }

    @Component({template: `<my-app></my-app>`})
    class Root {
    }

    @NgModule({
      declarations: [Root, AppComponent, Dynamic],
      exports: [Root, AppComponent, Dynamic],
      entryComponents: [Root, AppComponent, Dynamic]
    })
    class AppModule {
    }

    TestBed.configureTestingModule({imports: [AppModule]});
    let bootstrapCmp: Type<any> = AppComponent;
    // Turns out that if we bootstrap `AppComponent` `appComponent._vcRef.insert(cmptRef.hostView);`
    // does not work as no DOM gets inserted for `Dynamic`. Wrapping the test case in additional
    // component (`Root`) makes this work. This behavior is not correct as no `Root` should be
    // needed.
    // bootstrapCmp = Root; // uncommenting this makes this test pass.
    const fixture = TestBed.createComponent(bootstrapCmp);
    let appComponent!: AppComponent;
    fixture.detectChanges();

    const cmptRef =
        appComponent._cfr.resolveComponentFactory(Dynamic).create(appComponent._injector);
    appComponent._vcRef.insert(cmptRef.hostView);
    expect((fixture.nativeElement as HTMLElement).outerHTML).toContain('DYNAMIC COMPONENT');
  });
```

## üî• Exception or Error

I would expect that root (or dynamic components) should be able to insert children into their corresponding `ViewContainerRef`s 


